---
import InvestLayout from '../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import Disclosure from '../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout
  title="AI Computer"
  titleVi="AI Computer"
  description="Nguyen AI Computer — a specialized cloud AI Computer with a four-layer architecture, Agent team, Super Apps, and Model Mesh."
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">AI Computer</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Máy tính AI</p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-ink-muted max-w-3xl">
      Each user owns a private AI Computer Instance with multi-model intelligence, an Agent team, tools, memory, a data vault, workflows, evidence, approval gates, and a secure execution environment.
      <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">Mỗi người dùng sở hữu một Instance AI Computer riêng tư với trí tuệ đa mô hình, đội Agent, công cụ, bộ nhớ, kho dữ liệu, quy trình, bằng chứng, cổng phê duyệt và môi trường thực thi an toàn.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Four-layer architecture -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Four-Layer Architecture</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-8" lang="vi">Kiến trúc bốn lớp</p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border-l-4 border-l-gold">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gold uppercase">Platform</span>
            <span class="text-ink-dim">|</span>
            <code class="text-sm text-gold">nguyenai.net</code>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-ink">Nguyen AI Computer — Independent Platform</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">Independent backend, API gateway, auth, billing, agent team, model routing, memory, tools, workflows, and evidence. Fully self-sufficient.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border-l-4 border-l-gold">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gold uppercase">Academy</span>
            <span class="text-ink-dim">|</span>
            <code class="text-sm text-gold">edu.nguyenai.net</code>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-ink">Academy & Certification</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">Free AI learning for subscribers, certification programs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Agent team -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Agent Team</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-8" lang="vi">Đội Agent</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          { name: 'Nguyen Guide', vi: 'Nguyễn Guide', desc: 'Primary assistant and onboarding' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Researcher', vi: 'Nguyễn Researcher', desc: 'Heritage and historical research' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Archivist', vi: 'Nguyễn Archivist', desc: 'Document and artifact management' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Verifier', vi: 'Nguyễn Verifier', desc: 'Evidence verification and labeling' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Family Steward', vi: 'Nguyễn Family Steward', desc: 'Family tree and living-person privacy' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Founder', vi: 'Nguyễn Founder', desc: 'Founder OS and business tools' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Business Operator', vi: 'Nguyễn Business Operator', desc: 'Business operations and automation' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Global Connector', vi: 'Nguyễn Global Connector', desc: 'Diaspora networking and chapters' },
          { name: 'Nguyen Guardian', vi: 'Nguyễn Guardian', desc: 'Security, privacy, and safety' },
        ].map((agent) => (
          <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-lg p-4 card-hover">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink text-sm">{agent.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-ink-dim" lang="vi">{agent.vi}</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-2">{agent.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Super Apps -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Super Apps</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-8" lang="vi">Siêu ứng dụng</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
        {['AI Office', 'AI Research', 'AI Browser', 'AI Content', 'AI Media', 'AI Code', 'AI Automation', 'AI Founder OS', 'AI Business OS', 'AI Sales', 'AI Finance Workspace', 'AI Legal Workspace', 'Nguyen Roots', 'Nguyen Memory', 'Nguyen Knowledge', 'Nguyen Trust', 'Nguyen Network', 'Nguyen Founders', 'Nguyen Chapter OS'].map((app) => (
          <div class="bg-bg-soft border border-bg-border rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm text-ink-muted text-center card-hover">
            {app}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Model Mesh -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Model Mesh</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Model Mesh</p>
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm">
          The Model Mesh routes requests across multiple AI models — selecting the optimal model per task based on cost, latency, capability, and privacy requirements. Users are not locked into a single vendor; the mesh adapts as the model landscape evolves.
          <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">Model Mesh định tuyến yêu cầu qua nhiều mô hình AI — chọn mô hình tối ưu theo nhiệm vụ dựa trên chi phí, độ trễ, năng lực và yêu cầu quyền riêng tư.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
